  "texts": [
    "The course staff does not need significant training on the LLM-side of things, and can instead focus on generating the ground truth information in a natural way.",
    "Indeed, we simply used a textbook that we had written for one of our courses as a portion of the ground truth, and this textbook was written well before the chatbot was created.",
    "No specific methodology was followed to write it other than to ensure it was adequate for student learning, but the LLM was able to provide high-quality, aligned outputs based on it.Second, RAG is commonly used and several excellent open-source libraries have been created that easily integrated with other web technologies.",
    "See, for example, ChromaDB, which is the system we have used in our chatbot [10].",
    "We have found that the archiving and retrieval stages of a RAG system are computationally inexpensive as well."
